	<chapter>
		<title>Quiz selection</title>
		<section>
		<title>Introduction</title>
			<body>		
			<p>These questions are intended to ensure a depthful understanding of Gentoo as a whole
			and specific development situations that you will likely encounter during your time as
			a Gentoo developer. It's perfectly acceptable to ask your mentor or other knowledgable
			individuals for assistance. When completed, answers should be mailed to
			<mail link="recruiters@gentoo.org">recruiters</mail> along with other items mentioned on
			<uri>http://www.gentoo.org/proj/en/devrel/recruiters/index.xml</uri>.
			</p>
			</body>
		</section>
		<section>
		<title>Quiz selection</title>
			<body>
			<p>Developers who will have commit access to the Portage tree and/or will be performing
			ebuild development or maintainance tasks should take the <uri link="ebuild-quiz.txt">ebuild quiz</uri>.
			</p>
			<p>Developers who will be strictly working on infrastructure, GLSAs, or other non-ebuild areas of the project
			and will not have commit access to the Portage tree should take the <uri link="staff-quiz.txt">staff quiz</uri>.
			</p>
			</body>
		</section>
